lead_paragraph: Kristina King matched her career high with 16 points and grabbed a career-best nine rebounds and No. 16 West Virginia held off Mississippi 66-61 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: King Helps No. 16 West Virginia Women Hang on Versus Rebels
